<div class="well">
  <p>
    This site aims to bring together facts and figures about the current and previous iterations of the <em>Anime Saimoe Tournament</em>&mdash;a competition to find the most moe character of the year, organised by users of Japanese message board <%= link_to '2ch', 'http://www.2ch.net' %>.
  </p>
  <p>
    This is not the official Saimoe site, nor is it responsible for the running of the tournament. The official Saimoe 2014 site is <%= link_to 'here', 'http://www.saimoe2014.info/' %>, but is in Japanese only. Many thanks to Anonymous of the <%= link_to 'unofficial English Saimoe site', 'http://www.animesaimoe.org' %>, from which the data on this site is collected.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>Update 2014-11-20</strong>
  </p>
  <p>
    You may have noticed no results have been posted here&mdash;this is because the matches have been delayed by the tournament administrator's computer breaking. Hopefully the tournament will resume soon, but all of the matches yet to run (Last 16 onwards) will be delayed until an unspecified date in the future.
  </p>
</div>

<div class="container-fluid">
  <div class="row-fluid">
    <div class="span6 home-match-container">
      <% if @most_recent_view_models.any? %>
        <div class="page-header">
          <h3>Most Recent <%= 'Result'.pluralize(@most_recent_view_models.size) %></h3>
          <% if @late_message %>
            <br /><small><%= @late_message %></small>
          <% end %>
        </div>
        <%= render partial: 'view_models/match',
                   collection: @most_recent_view_models,
                   as: :vm %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
    <div class="span6 home-match-container">
      <% if @todays_match_view_models %>
        <div class="page-header">
          <h3>Today's <%= 'Match'.pluralize(@todays_match_view_models.size) %></h3>
        </div>
        <%= render partial: 'view_models/match',
                   collection: @todays_match_view_models,
                   as: :vm %>
      <% elsif @next_match_date %>
        <div class="page-header">
          <h3>Coming Up</h3>
        </div>
        <h4>Next match on <%= @next_match_date.to_s(:long) %></h4>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="cb"></div>

<hr />

<% if @tournament_view_model %>
  <%= render partial: 'view_models/tournament',
             object: @tournament_view_model,
             as: :vm %>
<% end %>
